      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Honest Deal on a Project Car \u2014 Priced Right! This vehicle is in poor condition, and we're being upfront about it \u2014 it will need repairs before it's road-ready. That said, it's a great opportunity for a handy DIY mechanic, someone looking for a parts source, or a budget buyer willing to put in some work. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, just a straightforward deal at a fair price!",
